{"tid":2461544,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"奶共陳奕迅又名「單春」 只剩一粒睾丸","createTime":"2021-03-25T12:34:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-25T12:39:00.000Z","uid":2054,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d8d35afd2be1ebc6ffebe261995c73ef2d4bed11","tid":2461544,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T12:34:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/entertainment/20130421/photo/0421-00282-051b1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20130421%2Fphoto%2F0421-00282-051b1.jpg&h=232164b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n歌手陳奕迅（Eason）每次開騷都又唱又跳，傾力演出，但說到最經典，莫過於早年他在台灣的「爆蛋」演出。2002年四月，Eason出席台北某校園演唱會，在「安哥」時段踩斷音箱支架，右腳意外失足墮台，下體卡在舞台邊，右睾丸慘被撞破，Eason惟有強忍痛楚，繼續獻唱，騷後才趕往急症室求診。<br />\nEason經一小時的去瘀手術後，仍須入院留醫五天，出院時要坐輪椅現身，上保母車一刻更瞇眼兼青筋盡現，「男人最痛」的一面表露無遺。幸院方表示其生殖能力未受影響，2004年更與老婆徐濠縈成功誕下女兒陳康堤，但自始Eason卻被網民獲封「單丸人」、「單蛋」及「爆袋迅」等抵死稱號。"},{"pid":"9f267ef2a0dbaf974edb9ec17153e87d3b1a32ca","tid":2461544,"uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T12:35:33.000Z","msg":"幾時爆埋另一邊呢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZxPxqGcwJbuRbt8bfjLGm386z5Qas4Y7S57d1JvdGB86?filename=5tWQPzG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5tWQPzG.jpg&h=0e943d83&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2ca40bb73cbeb6171887a3af6cb508043ea55c0f","tid":2461544,"uid":59221,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T12:36:36.000Z","msg":"殘忍的單丸非你專利<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ce5ed895416b8cc94bbc5c67ecb04c386bbdd17","tid":2461544,"uid":36894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T12:38:40.000Z","msg":"爆蛋都仲唱到歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a406afe9ee6a2dbd4437c50668ce20fed6378a70","tid":2461544,"uid":271545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T12:39:00.000Z","msg":"單丸也是正常"}]}